data.description: Assumable VA Loan Offered!      Welcome to Your Private Oasis! This inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home sits majestically on an expansive lot spanning almost an acre, offering an idyllic blend of comfort, space, and serenity. With its new roof, fully fenced yard, and a 2-car garage, this property is the epitome of easy living and modern convenience. As you approach the property, the classic brick facade immediately commands attention, exuding timeless appeal and durability. The lush, manicured front yard welcomes you, setting the tone for the pristine beauty that awaits inside. Upon stepping through the front door, you'll be greeted by an airy and open floor plan, where the living spaces flow seamlessly together. The spacious living room, illuminated by natural light, is perfect for entertaining or relaxing by the cozy fireplace. The adjacent kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances and ample cabinetry, The adjoining dining area offers a delightful space for family dinners and gatherings. The master suite is a true retreat, boasting generous proportions, a private en-suite bathroom offering a spa-like experience, complete with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide versatility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. Step outside to discover your own slice of paradise. The fully fenced backyard offers a safe and private haven for children and pets to play freely. With almost an acre of land, the possibilities are endless. You can create your dream garden, set up a playground, or even add a pool - the choice is yours! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful brick home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the timeless elegance, modern comforts, and spacious living that awaits you in this Beulah gem!
